Reviews: Tacos are amazing, but the seafood in particular the aguachile is amazing. The food has great flavor and service is impecable.
Relevant Content: *Tacos are amazing *seafood in particular the aguachile is amazing *The food has great flavor
Replies: * Amazing tacos and seafood * Great flavor in food

Reviews: On August 2018, Juan and his team fed 100 hungry people on my daughter's birthday party. I was able to choose four (4) different meats (Asada, Chorizo con Papa, Pastor & Chicken) plus the Salsas, Aguas Frescas, rice, beans, etc....All were delicious! I was delighted with their service, food quality, taste, and professionalism. I will hire Taquisas Los Juanes for future needs for sure! Recommended 100%
Replies: * Delicious food * High quality and taste

Reviews: We hired Los Juanes for my daughter's birthday and everyone loved their tacos. Every meat was delicious!  The aguas frescas were delicious! The beans. The rice.  Everything was great!  The service was awesome, and they're reasonably priced!  Everyone at the party loved the tacos they even got up for 2nds! I highly recommend them!
Relevant Content: *everyone loved their tacos *Every meat was delicious *The aguas frescas were delicious *The beans *The rice *Everything was great *Everyone at the party loved the tacos and even got up for 2nds
Replies: * Tacos loved by everyone * Delicious meat and aguas frescas * Great beans and rice * Guests went for seconds

Reviews: I hired Los Juanes for a birthday party a few weeks back and the food was delicious! The staff is very professional yet fun at the same time. They are also very clean which is a huge deal for me. I was a little nervous to hire them because they had just started up not too long ago but I have no regrets. I loved how they had a variety of different items that they offer, not just tacos. I will definitely hire them again!
Relevant Content: *the food was delicious *variety of different items offered, not just tacos
Replies: * Delicious food * Variety of items, not just tacos

Reviews: Hired Juan last weekend for a birthday party. He was professional and prices are reasonable. Best of all food was delicious. 2 of our guests already asked for his contact info.

Summary: The reviews about the food quality at Taquisas Los Juanes are overwhelmingly positive. Customers raved about the amazing tacos, seafood, and the great flavors in their dishes. The food is noted to be delicious, with high quality and taste. Many people enjoyed the variety of items on the menu, beyond just tacos. The tacos were loved by everyone, as well as the meat, aguas frescas, beans, and rice, which prompted guests to go for seconds. Overall, the sentiment towards the food quality at Taquisas Los Juanes is highly favorable.
